Submit to Indagationes Mathematicae, Prof. Jaap Korevaar 100-th
  birthday special issue, 32 pages, no figures, keywords:Lebesgue constants;
  Marcinkiewicz-Zygmund inequalities; Fejer points; Conformal Mapping

9 pages (without references and appendix), 17 figures, 25 Pages
  (total), Project website with code:
